{"tid":646991,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"改詞，原創： 棟人的薯片","createTime":"2018-04-29T13:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T07:49:08.000Z","uid":182001,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"51d40a1ce9a8e35f2229a7f72efc561319d0be33","tid":646991,"uid":182001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:24:24.000Z","msg":"--------------------<br />\n《怯. 你就輸一世》<br />\n原曲：#怯 #容祖兒<br />\n改詞： 大B x 吹瘋 <br />\n<br />\n奀星要求看戲專心 你別嘈住我<br />\n袁豪怕怕　發出聲音佢已聽得太多<br />\n怎麼可能 吔嘢會無聲音 發怒全為我<br />\n難怪你　暗星乜水 免費飛可笑麼<br />\n<br />\n期待你收聲散開 <br />\n煩著自己也都感覺無奈<br />\n恐怕太多 不實轉載<br />\n怪事明日 也許公開<br />\n這麼不知所謂 太感概<br />\n<br />\n聯盟還沒有觀看 便有嗌交戰<br />\n辣著棟仁便發現<br />\n傻得你掛住 戲外食筒薯片<br />\n偉豪你會在眼前<br />\n為何還沒有吵架 亂去與你開戰 <br />\n網上面臨你考驗<br />\n<br />\n投一次訴 罵你沒大紅條件<br />\n勞嘈全是你問題 沒發言<br />\n明知單挑驚險　<br />\n罵戰還未上演<br />\n薯片真的膚淺　怎麼我要忍你殘念<br />\n沒友善 什麼都怯<br />\n----------------------"},{"pid":"62f20d17d6e7d031e09c60403d6577b4795579b7","tid":646991,"uid":6674,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"邊間教會"},{"pid":"6531b01d7a169d8f1114f71afaaaa47934a2ea32","tid":646991,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:34:47.000Z","msg":"所以你覺得食薯片冇錯？"},{"pid":"1334bcc7e0480b67612a58b4e79cd695a3e06ac1","tid":646991,"uid":172915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:38:00.000Z","msg":"好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346508eb522ff69b236e52d82a22c243d254ee1d","tid":646991,"uid":110876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"搵返袁偉豪唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0d697336ffe518534233fc20a01e0283476789","tid":646991,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T16:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69143e2f303b0430d79f7bec718ae269e6011363","